thread.title: Sheeba

author: Sheeba
title: Sheeba
text: Have had a fantastic experience dealing with both Nick and Jess during the sale of our property. They always kept us updated during all stages of the sale, were very patient and transparent at all times. Fantastic outcome and the most stress free house sale ever! Highly recommend them...always professional and very approachable. Best of all, they know what they are doing and worked tirelessly to get the best outcome.
